Aurèle Barrière & Nathan Thomasset
7 colors game
ARCSYS 2 


This directory contains our project for ARCSYS2.
Run 'make' in the src/ directory, then execute 7colors.
You will be asked a number of games and what strategy to use.
If you use player's choice, the board will be printed each turn.
At the end, you will see the number of games won for each player.

For the report, see the doc/ directory. You can run make.sh to compile it, but a pre-compiled .pdf is included.



$ cd src/
$ make
$ ./7colors


Dependencies :
	     gcc
	     make
	     pdflatex (if you want to compile the report)